= License & Disclaimer =

(% class="box infomessage" %)
(((
**TL;DR: Open code, open data, open reasoning.**
FactHarbor uses a multi-license model to ensure our code (**AGPL/MIT**), documentation (**CC BY-SA**), and data (**ODbL**) remain public assets. Our mission is to prevent black-box proprietary control of truth-seeking tools.
)))

== 🚀 Quick Start: I want to... ==

* **Reuse documentation** → [[Creative Commons BY-SA 4.0>>#HDocumentation]]
* **Build on the code** → [[MIT & AGPL-3.0 Rules>>#HCode]]
